This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=3786

Add useful information to the statusline like:

 - buffer number
 - file type
 - file encoding
 - syntax errors (integration with Syntastic)
 - indentation errors (mixed indentation, expand tab)
 - trailing white spaces
 - line number / total lines
 - scroll position
 - integration with Fugitive (git)
 - etc...

Project repository and screenshots: https://github.com/millermedeiros/vim-statline
